  "title": "Personal Trainer and Sports Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will deliver expert sports massage therapy and training services, applying your skills to enhance client well-being and performance. Manage client sessions independently within a flexible half-day schedule at Upper Thomson Road.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>EEnsuringProvidingsmoothoperationsandneatworkspaceshared</li><li>Deliver professional sports massage therapy to clients, applying techniques that improve physical recovery and performance</li><li>Manage client appointments efficiently within designated half-day shifts to maximize service delivery</li><li>Utilize the studio space to conduct freelance training sessions, coordinating client access, bookings, and entry fee collection</li><li>Engage clients with a positive and welcoming attitude, contributing to a supportive and enjoyable studio environment</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Upper Thomson Road</li><li>Work Schedule: Choose one of the following half-day shifts: 5 half days (2:30pm–7:30pm) or 4 half days (3:30pm–8:30pm)</li><li>Compensation: Commission-based with incentives, minimum guaranteed remuneration of S$2,000</li><li>Studio Perk: Opportunity to use studio space for freelance client training (only clients pay entry fee)</li><li>Studio Culture: Must love cats 😺💕</li></ul>",
